Inclusion of Minasligas 


In the final determination, the Department found that Minasligas had a zero dumping margin. In consequence, the Department
excluded Minasligas from the results of the investigation, and instructed the Customs Service to terminate suspension
of liquidation for all entries of FeSi from Minasligas and to release any bond or other security and to refund any cash
