A. Within thirty (30) days after the date this order becomes final, distribute to each ASI member, affiliate, chapter,
organizational subdivision, or other entity associated directly or indirectly with ASI, copies of: (1) This order,
(2) the accompanying complaint, (3) appendix A to this order, (4) and any document that ASI revises pursuant to this
order, with the exception of the annual Membership List; and

