public version will be issued thereafter, pursuant to section 207.21 of the Commission's rules. 


Hearing



The Commission will hold a hearing in connection with these investigations beginning at 9:30 a.m. on April 12, 1994,
at the U.S. International Trade Commission Building. Requests to appear at the hearing should be filed in writing
with the Secretary to the Commission on or before April 4, 1994. A nonparty who has testimony that may aid the Commission's
