(b) the title of the final determination for which judicial review is sought, the investigating authority that issued
the final determination, the file number assigned by the investigating authority and, if the final determination
was published in an official publication, the appropriate citation, including the date of publication; and 
(c) the date on which the notice of the final determination was received by the other Party if the final determination
was not published in an official publication. 


